KCB Bank Tanzania Limited, bụkwa KCB Bank Tanzania, bụ ụlọ akụ azụmaahịa na Tanzania

Ọ bụ otu n'ime ụlọ akụ iri abụọ na itoolu (29) nyere ikike nke Bank of Tanzania, onye na-ahụ maka ụlọ akụ nke obodo ahụ. Ụlọ akụ ahụ bụ onye otu Kenya Commercial Bank (KCB Group), nke dị na Nairobi, Kenya, yana ndị enyemaka na Kenya, Rwanda, South Sudan, Tanzania na Uganda..
